01:20:59,356 --> 01:21:00,664
The Druze, the Yehidi, the Muslims.

1069
01:21:00,724 --> 01:21:02,294
And none of these
religions condone it.

1070
01:21:02,993 --> 01:21:04,267
Farah, what are you saying?

1071
01:21:07,197 --> 01:21:09,143
It's neither Asian nor Islamic.

1072
01:21:10,133 --> 01:21:13,080
The roots of this practice lie
in an ancient tribal code..

1073
01:21:13,136 --> 01:21:15,013
..And it's followed by
people the world over.

1074
01:21:15,172 --> 01:21:16,708
It predates Islam.

1075
01:21:18,275 --> 01:21:19,720
An ancient code?

1076
01:21:21,111 --> 01:21:23,113
So ingrained in
these people's heads..

1077
01:21:23,180 --> 01:21:25,421
..They don't even
realise they still follow it.

1078
01:21:25,649 --> 01:21:28,823
Miss Siddiqui, please
do not mock my client.

1079
01:21:30,420 --> 01:21:33,094
A code that promotes
killing your daughter?

1080
01:21:33,223 --> 01:21:36,067
The woman is responsible
for the honour of the tribe.

1081
01:21:37,127 --> 01:21:39,664
She carries their future in her womb.

1082
01:21:40,230 --> 01:21:42,938
That's why relationships
need to be controlled.

1083
01:21:44,001 --> 01:21:45,674
A woman must be protected.

1084
01:21:47,271 --> 01:21:50,377
God forbid lose
women taint good blood.

1085
01:21:50,807 --> 01:21:53,913
Miss Siddiqui, this
is my final warning!

1086
01:21:54,678 --> 01:21:56,919
So it's a way of
regulating sexual relations.

1087
01:21:56,980 --> 01:22:01,986
Yes. Only the strongest
most trustworthy survive.

1088
01:22:02,052 --> 01:22:03,963
It was true of Middle Age England.

1089
01:22:04,821 --> 01:22:08,359
The people in the village would marry
each other to keep the blood pure,

1090
01:22:08,592 --> 01:22:11,402
..to protect itself from outsiders,
from strangers.

1091
01:22:11,628 --> 01:22:12,800
Yes. Exactly.

1092
01:22:13,363 --> 01:22:15,400
It's happened everywhere
at one time or the other.

1093
01:22:16,333 --> 01:22:21,749
A woman has always been and still
is man's most precious possession.

1094
01:22:26,643 --> 01:22:29,954
Zar, zan, zameen.

1095
01:22:33,116 --> 01:22:34,220
What's that?

1096
01:22:37,287 --> 01:22:38,561
The code.

1097
01:22:44,161 --> 01:22:45,606
What does it mean?

1098
01:22:46,930 --> 01:22:49,911
A man may kill to
protect three things.

1099
01:22:50,167 --> 01:22:51,976
Land, Gold and..

1100
01:22:56,139 --> 01:22:57,243
And?

1101
01:23:03,847 --> 01:23:05,019
Women.

1102
01:23:15,225 --> 01:23:20,106
Nazir, just give me
permission to handle the situation.

1103
01:23:22,833 --> 01:23:25,939
We'll reclaim everything we've lost.

1104
01:23:29,673 --> 01:23:32,552
Do what you feel is
right Riyaaz bhai.

1105
01:23:33,744 --> 01:23:37,089
I have nothing left to give.

1106
01:23:54,865 --> 01:23:56,936
I think my uncle is
trying to hurt us.

1107
01:23:59,136 --> 01:24:00,240
Why?

1108
01:24:04,808 --> 01:24:05,980
Is it because of this?

1109
01:24:06,910 --> 01:24:08,218
He has threatened to kill me Sir.

1110
01:24:09,846 --> 01:24:11,154
How old are you miss?

1111
01:24:13,950 --> 01:24:15,054
17.

1112
01:24:18,855 --> 01:24:19,959
<i>I'm 21.</i>

1113
01:24:20,791 --> 01:24:22,236
Are you sure they weren't just angry?

1114
01:24:22,793 --> 01:24:25,399
Angry?
He's threatened to kill us Sir.

1115
01:24:26,797 --> 01:24:28,276
They're not horrible people.

1116
01:24:33,336 --> 01:24:34,815
They're just looking after you.

1117
01:24:35,405 --> 01:24:36,850
In a round about way.

1118
01:24:38,375 --> 01:24:39,683
I guess.

1119
01:24:43,080 --> 01:24:46,152
I see this as a domestic
issue which will be resolved.

1120
01:24:47,851 --> 01:24:52,891
At the moment, I can only give you
the address of the nearest shelter..

1121
01:24:53,290 --> 01:24:56,703
..That might be able to provide
you temporary accommodation and food.

1122
01:24:57,127 --> 01:24:59,403
But I would suggest,
you call you family.

1123
01:25:00,230 --> 01:25:01,709
They must be worried.

1124
01:25:05,235 --> 01:25:09,183
You can't offer us any
protection incase they show up?

1125
01:25:10,140 --> 01:25:12,086
Unfortunately I can't.

1126
01:25:14,077 --> 01:25:15,715
I'm sure you'll be fine.

1127
01:25:21,118 --> 01:25:22,688
What are you going to do?

1128
01:25:24,755 --> 01:25:26,735
She has betrayed our trust.

1129
01:25:28,158 --> 01:25:30,069
Saira leaves us no choice.

1130
01:25:31,928 --> 01:25:34,204
Don't worry about the
consequences Riyaaz bhai.

1131
01:25:34,264 --> 01:25:36,005
You can leave for India tomorrow.

1132
01:25:36,733 --> 01:25:39,111
We'll get Nazir the
best lawyers in town.

1133
01:25:39,236 --> 01:25:40,977
He'll get 15 years maximum.

1134
01:25:46,643 --> 01:25:47,815
And for a child?

1135
01:25:47,878 --> 01:25:49,255
Even less.

1136
01:25:59,990 --> 01:26:01,628
The court has just
let me know that..

1137
01:26:01,691 --> 01:26:03,830
..Your case is going to
be heard in 3 weeks time.

1138
01:26:07,697 --> 01:26:08,801
And.

1139
01:26:12,869 --> 01:26:14,371
What happens after that?

1140
01:26:16,106 --> 01:26:17,449
You'll serve your term.

1141
01:26:18,441 --> 01:26:21,285
We will use the code
in your mitigation.

1142
01:26:23,313 --> 01:26:26,920
Do you realise that your social
conditioning is so strong that..

1143
01:26:26,983 --> 01:26:29,361
..Even after all this you
still can't think for yourself?

1144
01:26:33,990 --> 01:26:36,027
That's enough Farah. We should go.

1145
01:26:40,931 --> 01:26:42,342
I do realize that.

1146
01:26:46,403 --> 01:26:48,007
It's people like you..

1147
01:26:48,405 --> 01:26:51,409
..Make life
difficult for the rest of us.

1148
01:27:02,118 --> 01:27:03,188
What do you think?

1149
01:27:04,888 --> 01:27:06,094
I don't know Saira.

1150
01:27:09,359 --> 01:27:10,770
I just don't know.

1151
01:27:15,165 --> 01:27:16,405
Will it make you happy?

1152
01:27:38,989 --> 01:27:40,093
Thanks very much!

1153
01:27:44,928 --> 01:27:46,373
Well an ancient code.

1154
01:27:47,597 --> 01:27:50,407
Who would have thought. Well done!

1155
01:27:51,835 --> 01:27:53,178
It's a sad case though.

1156
01:27:53,803 --> 01:27:56,147
Mind you, he'll get
out after 7-10 years.

1157
01:27:57,040 --> 01:27:59,145
Fantastic, Mr. Timothy James.

1158
01:28:02,679 --> 01:28:03,783
Cheers!

1159
01:28:04,681 --> 01:28:05,751
I quit.

1160
01:28:06,049 --> 01:28:07,119
I beg your pardon?

1161
01:28:07,317 --> 01:28:08,694
I can't defend this man..

1162
01:28:10,053 --> 01:28:11,361
..And I can't work with you.

1163
01:28:11,755 --> 01:28:14,065
You're letting the stress
and the pressure get to you.

1164
01:28:14,291 --> 01:28:15,895
You're taking this
whole thing too personally.

1165
01:28:16,092 --> 01:28:18,197
That brother of his still roams free.

1166
01:28:19,095 --> 01:28:20,369
Saira could be here.

1167
01:28:20,430 --> 01:28:22,171
Don't put your
emotions in front of your job.

1168
01:28:22,232 --> 01:28:23,802
You always do that. I've told you.

1169
01:28:24,167 --> 01:28:27,910
We're getting a murdering
father off with just 15 years.

1170
01:28:28,905 --> 01:28:30,316
I've got blood on my hands.

1171
01:28:30,707 --> 01:28:31,708
You do too.

1172
01:28:31,775 --> 01:28:32,845
You're not serious.

1173
01:28:34,110 --> 01:28:35,987
I have to find my own way.

1174
01:28:40,283 --> 01:28:41,387
Farah!

1175
01:29:07,944 --> 01:29:09,014
Hello?

1176
01:29:11,881 --> 01:29:12,985
Baba?

1177
01:29:14,851 --> 01:29:15,989
Saira.

1178
01:29:18,188 --> 01:29:19,394
I miss you Baba.

1179
01:29:24,828 --> 01:29:25,966
Come home, sweetheart.

1180
01:29:29,165 --> 01:29:30,235
David?

1181
01:29:35,939 --> 01:29:37,043
Bring him.

1182
01:29:37,907 --> 01:29:39,045
We'll be waiting.

1183
01:29:43,279 --> 01:29:44,587
Ok Baba.

1184
01:29:48,118 --> 01:29:49,222
Bye.

1185
01:29:50,086 --> 01:29:51,190
Bye.

1186
01:30:50,146 --> 01:30:52,285
If I stay here.

1187
