If I just stay here.

1188
01:30:57,353 --> 01:30:58,764
<i>L</i> just lay.

1189
01:30:58,822 --> 01:31:00,165
Lay here.

1190
01:31:00,356 --> 01:31:05,328
Would you lie with me
and just forget the world.

1191
01:31:21,744 --> 01:31:23,018
I didn't know you sing.

1192
01:31:24,280 --> 01:31:27,625
There are lots of things
about me you still don't know.

1193
01:31:27,884 --> 01:31:30,194
Well I can't wait to find out.

1194
01:31:34,824 --> 01:31:36,895
If I just lay.

1195
01:31:38,828 --> 01:31:42,071
If I just lay here.

1196
01:31:42,799 --> 01:31:48,044
Would you lie with me
and just forget the world.

1197
01:32:30,113 --> 01:32:31,217
Baba!

1198
01:32:33,783 --> 01:32:34,853
Baba!

1199
01:32:35,618 --> 01:32:36,790
I missed you, Baba.

1200
01:32:37,654 --> 01:32:38,792
Baba!

1201
01:32:41,291 --> 01:32:42,668
Baba. I missed you, Baba.

1202
01:32:51,834 --> 01:32:53,871
Everyone is waiting for you.

1203
01:32:54,971 --> 01:32:57,679
Go inside, I'll speak to
David and follow you in.

1204
01:32:59,008 --> 01:33:00,078
Okay, Baba.

1205
01:33:07,183 --> 01:33:09,720
Ma?

1206
01:33:10,253 --> 01:33:12,392
Baba!!

1207
01:33:13,790 --> 01:33:15,360
Saira! Saira!

1208
01:33:15,758 --> 01:33:19,296
Saira, get the..

1209
01:33:20,730 --> 01:33:21,834
Saira!

1210
01:33:48,891 --> 01:33:49,995
Saira!

1211
01:33:56,666 --> 01:33:58,612
What are you doing with sister?

1212
01:34:03,940 --> 01:34:05,715
Saira.

1213
01:34:05,875 --> 01:34:07,081
No. Saira.

1214
01:34:07,310 --> 01:34:08,687
Saira.

1215
01:34:39,842 --> 01:34:43,619
Pry open my sealed lips,
I want to speak.

1216
01:34:44,881 --> 01:34:48,294
Break open these shackles
around my wrists, I want to seek.

1217
01:34:50,019 --> 01:34:53,762
That noble purpose I had once,
A long way from here.

1218
01:34:55,358 --> 01:34:59,397
Let me give myself to those winds,
And get rid of all this fear

1219
01:35:00,697 --> 01:35:04,702
I had begged for you, At every altar.

1220
01:35:06,169 --> 01:35:10,914
With hopeful prayer,
with tearful plea.

1221
01:35:12,208 --> 01:35:13,778
Can I measure you now
against all those wishes?

1222
01:35:14,277 --> 01:35:16,985
And break open these
shackles around me?

1223
01:35:17,914 --> 01:35:22,090
Let me give myself to the wind,
